name: B//W # 13/19
description: A new viewpoint to my abstract art process in all black and white. Each style was created a different way and each one challenging the mind to see past face value and to discover what lies on the inside. This particular piece was inspired by my fascination with the structure of viruses. This entire collection has more meaning and messaging to it than any of my other work to date. Each image is a 2048 x 2048 1/1 jpg image.
